data.description: At last - this is the one you have been waiting for!  This must see single story, approx 1500 sf home features 3 bed 2 bath. 2 car attached garage. RV parking pad and additional boat, trailer or vehicle parking. Beautiful built in 12'x 34' pool max 6 ft deep with new energy efficient pumps for pool pump & waterfalls. Large open kitchen with lots of counter space and cabinets, new stainless steel appliances included with sale. Dining bar and dining room area. New luxury vinyl flooring throughout livingroom and kitchen. Cozy wood burning stove in livingroom. This LEVEL .6 AC parcel has a fenced front yard with entry gate and lawn, pool is fenced in back. Side yards are fully fenced and currently used for chickens and goats. New oversized HVAC installed in 2020. Freshened up paint outside & in. Located in Copper Cove this property includes access to Lake Tulloch with Boat Launch, Day use boat docks, swim beach & 7 acre Black Creek Park for very low dues. Discover all that Copperopolis has to offer. Just an hour to Bear Valley or Dodge Ridge for local snow skiing and snow play. A little over an hour to Yosemite National Park and just two hours from the bay area. Enjoy Murphys nearby for year round wine tasting and restaurants! Lots of nearby hiking trails, forests and scenic drives.
